<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950 to-slate-950 text-blue-50 h-full">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="mt-16">
            <span class="text-8xl font-bold leading-tight text-center border-b-8 border-indigo-800">Jeopardy-like</span>
            <br>
            <span class="text-8xl font-bold leading-tight text-center border-b-8 border-indigo-800">game maker</span>

            <div class="mt-8 max-w-[60%] mx-auto text-2xl text-center text-indigo-200 leading-relaxed">
                Create your own Jeopardy-like quiz game and play with your friends over discord, or your audience on Twitch or YouTube.
            </div>

            <a href="/jeopardy/create" class="block mt-8 mx-auto bg-indigo-800 w-64 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-md ring-2 ring-indigo-700 hover:ring-indigo-500 drop-shadow-xl shadow-lg">
                Create a game
            </a>

            <div class="mt-32 max-w-[50%] mx-auto text-indigo-200 leading-relaxed">
                Discover a simple and efficient way to host your own Jeopardy-style trivia game with our app, completely free!
                Tailor your game by creating categories and questions that suit your content and audience.
                Invite participants to join in real-time, making it perfect for live events or gatherings.

                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How It Works:</div>
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside max-w-[400px] mx-auto">
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-bold text-indigo-100">Create Your Game:</span>
                        Begin by customizing your Jeopardy-style game. Define categories, craft questions, and input answers that resonate with your friends or audience.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-bold text-indigo-100">Invite Participants:</span>
                        Share a link to the game to invite friends or viewers to join your trivia session.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-bold text-indigo-100">Enjoy the game:</span>
                        The app is designed to be user-friendly and transparent. Enjoy the streamlined game play experience while your friends follow along.
                    </li>
                </ol>

                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">More things coming soon</div>
                <div class="max-w-[400px] mx-auto">
                    The app is still under development. Stay tuned for more updates to the game and even new games.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-32 pb-4 text-indigo-300 text-center">
                Any feedback? Let us know at
                <a href="mailto:gm@adikus.me" class="text-indigo-200 hover:underline">gm@adikus.me</a>
                <br>
                Â© adikus | 2023
